71,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8280e2f08af366878510376eae26e5ea0791059","tid":2478022,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:40:22.000Z","msg":"介紹下graphql有咩好壞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:55:50.000Z","msg":"簡單黎講就係將個N+1 problem由frontend推左去backend<br />\ngraphql最重要係define左query個shape，可以explicitly決定返黎嘅data有咩fields<br />\n去到backend，最極限可以根據你嘅query去generate SQL query去join曬exactly你要嘅資料，一次DB query就搞掂。但就算多左fields，只要你無query到都唔會return返去frontend<br />\n而且因爲全部野都係explicitly typed，配合埋graphql-code-generator可以做到完美frontend-server-db typesafe，即係全部都有auto complete<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f34df9cc61b98361cfd15996b24d0147deff67f","tid":2478022,"uid":23094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:07:22.000Z","msg":"呢個Post實勁多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a187afabdc694011604d2a94e1d75d077b40b937","tid":2478022,"uid":2771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b94c7511525d6e195da0e5c974a64d049339dd80","tid":2478022,"uid":10207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:44:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n我覺得要精通react fullstack最緊要係常睇article同d maintainer 嘅blog post</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩途徑搵到，medium?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:15:19.000Z","msg":"我多數係reddit /r/reactjs /r/graphql<br />\n<br />\n有時redux個maintainer (/u/acemarke) 會上水糾正人用redux嘅錯誤<br />\n<br />\n有時redux個author兼react core member (Dan) 係twitter/blog會講d重要嘅大路concept，例如 <a href=\"https://overreacted.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foverreacted.io%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=c638db99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://overreacted.io/</a> 初期係爲左hook寫左幾篇，簡直係react hook葵花寶典 (<a href=\"https://overreacted.io/a-complete-guide-to-useeffect/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foverreacted.io%2Fa-complete-guide-to-useeffect%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=99925940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://overreacted.io/a-complete-guide-to-useeffect/</a>) (<a href=\"https://overreacted.io/making-setinterval-declarative-with-react-hooks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foverreacted.io%2Fmaking-setinterval-declarative-with-react-hooks%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=503f4c61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://overreacted.io/making-setinterval-declarative-with-react-hooks/</a>) <br />\n<br />\n比多個resource <a href=\"https://github.com/enaqx/awesome-react\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fenaqx%2Fawesome-react&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=a498cf75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/enaqx/awesome-react</a>"},{"pid":"b82a165ba88b71df67725b6981481b96298c8b1a","tid":2478022,"uid":2771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9f34df9cc61b98361cfd15996b24d0147deff67f","tid":2478022,"uid":23094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:07:22.000Z","msg":"呢個Post實勁多負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"唔緊要，推廣下交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1c9123f6cf552c298b24d5171c73a0716cea42","tid":2478022,"uid":16560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"有咩實際情況會用yield 同generator"},{"pid":"516f5f5a058589483d560bddeea5b94850f8f5f5","tid":2478022,"uid":2771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd1c9123f6cf552c298b24d5171c73a0716cea42","tid":2478022,"uid":16560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"有咩實際情況會用yield 同generator"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"如果你喺話redux-saga，我基本上唔會選擇用，因爲佢做到嘅野thunk都做到。saga用call咪即係await，put咪即係dispatch<img src=\"